<HEADLINE>
<P>
FEDERAL CONTRACT AWARDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Lockheed Aeronautical Systems Co. in Burbank won a $780,000 contract from the 
Navy to supply testing equipment used on P-3 aircraft. 
</P>
</TEXT>
