</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Edward Ehrman has been appointed international director of marketing for the 
diagnostics systems group at Beckman Instruments Inc., a Fullerton-based 
manufacturer of instruments for medical research and diagnosis. Elkie Eastman, 
speaking for Beckman, said Ehrman will coordinate marketing strategy from 
Fullerton. Ehrman, previously general manager for Beckman Instruments in Japan, 
