<TEXT>
<P>
Authorities today recovered the bodies of all 16 people killed in the crash of 
a plane carrying a U.S. congressional delegation headed by Rep. Mickey Leland 
(D-Tex.). 
</P>
<P>
A helicopter hovered near the face of a sheer cliff in southwestern Ethiopia as 
the bodies were hoisted up one by one from the rugged mountainside where the 
twin-engine plane crashed last week. 
</P>
